                Transportation
              


















UIC Transportation provides a variety of automotive services to the UIC campus community, including Intracampus bus routes, Night Ride, chauffeur service, departmental moving services, and rental/repair of university owned vehicles.
Our Mission: To provide safe, efficient, and barrier-free transit services that support the UIC community.
We encourage you to take advantage of the UIC Safe app that is available for your mobile device at no cost.
We also hope you will let us know how we’re doing by giving us feedback after your ride.
To contact us about any transportation issues or questions, please email rides@uic.edu.







Campus Transportation Services Resume







            Bus Service
          Heading link



 
Copy link












                            Buses and Shuttles
                    

                Bus schedules and route information for the Intracampus Buses.
            












                            Paratransit
                    

                Paratransit Service is available seven days a week for students, faculty, and staff with disabilities.
            












                            Night Ride
                    

                Transportation option offered after the operational hours of the campus bus circuit.
            












                            UI Ride
                    

                UI Ride is an intercampus shuttle that provides transportation between Chicago and Urbana-Champaign.
            












                            Campus Auto Rental Service
                    

                The Campus Auto Rental Service provides vehicles for use on university business.
            












                            Chauffeur Service
                    

                Chauffeur services are available to UIC faculty, staff and students.
            












                            Abandoned Bicycle Removal
                    

                Policy on the removal of abandoned bicycles.
            












                            Moving Service
                    

                All moving services can be requested by submitting a billable service request through FMWeb.
            












